<div id="review_3310762022" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3310762022" />
    <a title="David" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1385615-david"><img alt="David" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1611291805p2/1385615.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3310762022?book_show_action=true">May 03, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="David" class="user" itemprop="url" name="David" href="/user/show/1385615-david">David</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780140447866" href="/book/show/207992.Ward_No_6_and_Other_Stories_1892_1895">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3310762022" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14997445589703277118">Many claim that Chekhov was most successful when using the short story form. It turns out that I much prefer his plays. His theater pieces seem more expansive (some would say boring) and the philosophical messages are delivered more gently. The reader or audience member has more time to contemplate. The stories here felt heavy-handed, with their morals concentrated, obvious, and (ironically) overly dramatic.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review3310762022">
  <td colspan="2">
    <div class="updateActionLinks">
